{"tid":1580793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"何君堯：名下賽駒天祿將停賽直至動亂平息","createTime":"2019-09-19T08:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T11:57:00.000Z","uid":125349,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"44e42796067dfa08a1d2a519e1866f56940586f4","tid":1580793,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯發聲明，表示對昨日馬會取消比賽，對本港賽馬事業及馬迷造成損失深表遺憾。他與兩名合夥人商量後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">決定在動亂平息前，名下賽駒「天祿」會暫停參賽</span></span>，指相關決定是為了支持本港賽馬業健康發展、維護馬迷合法權益，及為了香港長期穩定安寧著想。何君堯又指，香港正常的社會秩序和安寧，不應受政治因素干擾和破壞，又指馬匹無罪，不能夠因為「天祿」有優異表現而剝奪牠馳騁賽場的權利。<br />\n<br />\n「天祿」原定昨晚參加跑馬地馬場賽馬日的首場賽事，有網民號召要入場「聲援」，馬會因安全考慮決定取消昨晚全部賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1174398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1174398&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5cv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=2763516c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1174398</a>"},{"pid":"49089f6a156516560c85465fafcc624c1ba2d223","tid":1580793,"uid":193436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T08:54:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec02e459c921470da4731f8448331d9d4620edeb","tid":1580793,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219727e6dcaffe2f2e304ac54d8e4361ab70601e","tid":1580793,"uid":185018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T08:54:55.000Z","msg":"馬匹無罪，何妖其罪"},{"pid":"3c57154868ec15fc7fd767c587e4f36d8cd55f60","tid":1580793,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"何君堯指鹿為馬"},{"pid":"381845c85924c95f865d9fdbe5c0